疫苗告诉我们“充满希望和欣快”的新专辑“Pick-Up Full Of Pink Carnations” https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-vaccines-new-album-pick-up-full-of-pink-carnations-interview-3500393?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-vaccines-new-专辑拾取充满粉红色康乃馨的采访Rhian DalyWed, 20 Sep 2023 10:00:31 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3500393 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="疫苗" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队还分享了他们的第一首歌曲“Heartbreak Kid”，并宣布 2024 年将进行新的英国和欧洲巡演</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-vaccines-new-album-pick-up-full-of-pink-carnations-interview-3500393">《疫苗》的帖子告诉我们“充满希望和欣快”的新专辑《Pick-Up Full Of Pink Carnations》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="疫苗" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/The-Vaccines-Credit-WRENNE-EVANS-LEAD-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-vaccines">疫苗乐队</a>宣布了他们的第六张专辑《Pick-Up Full Of Pink Carnations》的详细信息，并分享了他们的第一首单曲《Heartbreak Kid》，以及新的英国巡演的消息。请查看下面的全部内容以及我们对主唱贾斯汀·杨的采访。</p><p> 《Heartbreak Kid》是乐队自 2022 年发行 EP《Planet Of The Youth》以来的首张新作品，也是自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-vaccines-freddie-cowan-departs-band-for-foreseeable-future-3414169">原吉他手 Freddie Cowan 离开后的</a>首张专辑。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-vaccines-freddie-cowan-the-scenarios-pete-robertson-interview-3381266">The Vaccines 的 Freddie Cowan 谈论首张专辑 Freddie Cowan &amp; The Scenarios</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌以宽屏、澎湃的吉他和有力的、赞歌般的节奏部分详细描述了浪漫的失落——而杨则唱出了一段关系崩溃的故事。</p><p> “我不一定自称是主角，”他告诉<em>NME</em> 。 “整张唱片都是非常个人化和真实的，是经历过的和生活过的，但唱片上有一些歌曲非常直白，也有一些是故事。对于《心碎的孩子》，我认为它几乎做到了它在罐头上所说的。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="心碎的孩子" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GXpr_2Kx_tc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在单曲的副歌部分，主唱在标题的两种用法之间切换，首先是敦促：“<em>让你的心碎吧，孩子</em>。”后来，他把它改成了一个新的绰号，唱道：“<em>哦，你从没想过他们会离开你，但他们确实离开了/现在每个人都称你为心碎的孩子</em>。”</p><p> “有时我确实喜欢号召大家战斗，但我真的不知道我们这样做了多少次，因为也许很难做到正确，”杨说。 “但其中有一个微妙的翻转，我很喜欢。”</p><p>许多不同形式的损失助长了“拾取满满的粉红色康乃馨”——Young 表示，这一主题长期以来一直是 The Vaccines 的 DNA 的一部分。 “这不仅体现在我们的歌词中，也体现在我们的声音中，”他解释道。 “有一种怀旧感，看着后视镜，想知道你留下的东西是否比你正在走向的更好。</p><p> “这在歌词中非常明确，但在音乐中也是如此。它在旋律和声音中。这张唱片给人一种怀旧的感觉。关于我们的音乐，我多次说过，欣快感和忧郁感是同等重要的。我不认为这是一张悲伤或沮丧的唱片——实际上我认为它充满希望和欣快——但我确实认为它有忧郁的基调。”</p><p>这张专辑是在杨住在洛杉矶并经历自己的失落时期时创作的。尽管这张专辑严格来说并不是关于对美国现实的幻想破灭，但他说它使用了这种感觉作为“一种非常字面的、公开的隐喻，来表达一个人的期望与经历”。</p><p> “像洛杉矶或纽约，甚至伦敦这样的城市存在于每首歌、每本书、每部电影和每部电视节目中，”他说。 “我们认为这些地方将为我们提供避难所或逃生场所，或培养我们一直希望成为的人的环境。</p><p> “然后实际上，你会意识到，‘我是在奔向某事还是在逃避某事？事实上，即使我正在逃避某些事情，我是否能够逃避我正在逃避的事情？”</p><p> 《Pick-Up Full Of Pink Carnations》发现 The Vaccines 与 2021 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/the-vaccines-back-in-love-city-review-3041873">《Back In Love City》</a>和《Planet Of The Youth》的音乐风格彻底决裂，后者涵盖了从迪斯科到意大利西部片的各种风格。它已被更有机的东西所取代。回顾乐队的前一个时代，杨说他为乐队在这两张唱片上所取得的成就感到自豪，但他内心有些质疑他们是否充分利用了他们的成员。 </p><figure id="attachment_3500432" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3500432" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3500432" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-vaccines-community-2023.jpg" alt="2023 年疫苗社区节" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-vaccines-community-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-vaccines-community-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-vaccines-community-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-vaccines-community-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-vaccines-community-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-vaccines-community-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3500432" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年社区节上的疫苗 图片来源：Jack Hall/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “我们有一位令人难以置信、令人惊叹的摇滚鼓手 [Yoann Intonti]，我认识的每个和他一起演奏的人都说，‘这家伙疯了’，那么我们为什么要对所有的鼓进行编程呢？”他说。 “为什么我们要剥夺人性呢？蒂姆（兰纳姆）现在正在弹吉他，他是一位令人难以置信的、旋律优美的吉他手——你为什么不把它带到你所做的事情的前面呢？”</p><p>他补充说，现在感觉更难“创造出一些感觉自然、人性化和不完美的东西”，这表明这让他更倾向于现场鼓，“正在演奏的部分和正在演唱的台词，并且有更多的东西”音乐中的脆弱性和不完美”。 “I think that&#39;s ultimately why we&#39;re all drawn to music and musicians in the first place, right? And why AI will probably not triumph in that respect.”</p><p> That humanity and vulnerability was also recorded in LA, with The Vaccines teaming up with producer Andrew Wells ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/halsey">Halsey</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">Phoebe Bridgers</a> ). “We were in his home studio in the hills with this amazing view,” Young shared. “It was a very inspiring, exciting place to be every day and I think you can hear that too. The more we make records, the more I really value being somewhere with someone that makes you feel excited to be there.”</p><p> The band&#39;s sixth album marks a new era not just in sound, but in personnel too. It is the first Vaccines record not to feature original guitarist Freddie Cowan, who left the band last summer. “He actually left about two weeks before we flew to start recording,” Young explained. “There was maybe some trepidation going for all of us, wondering what that was going to be like.” Within 10 minutes of the sessions starting, though, they settled into their new roles and things “felt very natural and easy”. </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CxXzkH3ruvb/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" back